@page "/list-with-us"

<PageTitle>List Your Stallions — Stallions Nominations Marketplace</PageTitle>

<div class="lwu-hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>List Your Stallion's Nominations</h1>
        <p class="lwu-subtitle">
            Reach verified buyers across Australia. Manage fixed-price offerings and timed auctions
            from one dedicated dashboard — with every transaction handled securely through
            Stallions Australia.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container lwu-body">

    <section class="lwu-how">
        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <ol class="lwu-steps">
            <li>
                <span class="lwu-step-num">1</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Get in touch</strong>
                    <p>Contact Stallions Australia using the details below. We'll confirm your farm's details and set up your account.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="lwu-step-num">2</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>We onboard your farm</strong>
                    <p>We create your stud farm profile on the platform and give you access to the Stud Farm Admin dashboard.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="lwu-step-num">3</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Add your stallions and publish listings</strong>
                    <p>Upload stallion profiles, set your pricing, and publish fixed-price or auction listings — all from your dashboard.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="lwu-step-num">4</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Stallions Australia handles the rest</strong>
                    <p>We process the platform fee on each sale and issue binding records. You invoice the buyer directly for the nomination balance under your own terms.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="lwu-contact">
        <h2>Contact us to get started</h2>
        <div class="lwu-contact-cards">
            <div class="lwu-contact-card">
                <span class="lwu-contact-icon">✉</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Email</strong>
                    <a href="mailto:listings@stallionsaustralia.com.au">listings@stallionsaustralia.com.au</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lwu-contact-card">
                <span class="lwu-contact-icon">☎</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Phone</strong>
                    <a href="tel:+61000000000">+61 (0) 000 000 000</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="lwu-contact-note">
            We aim to respond within one business day. Please include your farm name and the stallions
            you intend to list so we can prepare your account.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="lwu-already">
        <p>Already set up? <a href="authentication/login">Sign in to your Admin Dashboard →</a></p>
    </section>

</div>
